&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SOLVA SURGERY - PEMBROKESHIRE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Require a Salaried Doctor (with view to Partnership)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;We are an established dispensing practice, situated in the idyllic harbour village of Solva on the beautiful coastline of Pembrokeshire.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic Salaried Doctor/Partner to join our friendly team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6-7 sessions per week – to start immediately (but we’re happy to wait for the right candidate).  Days flexible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 weeks annual leave + 1 week study &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purpose built premises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holistic family practice – Friendly, caring &amp; compassionate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities for teaching – We currently teach Swansea Medical Students&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High QOF achievement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2530 patients – Dispensing to 2300&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dedicated nursing and support staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fully computerized – Paperlight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to the Cluster Pharmacist and Occupational Therapist support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively engaged in MDT working with wider community team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Location - Beaches, coastal path, surfing, hiking and climbing etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please feel free to contact the practice with any queries you may have or if you want to arrange an informal visit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; For any queries please contact us at the surgery, either Dr Sujan Dhaduvai or Jayne Williams (Practice Manager).  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tel&lt;/strong&gt;:  01437 721306 / Jayne.williams28@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
